---

<!-- ═══════════ 2. HERO SECTION ═══════════ -->
<section
    class="hero relative min-h-screen flex items-center overflow-hidden"
    id="hero"
>
    <div class="hero-bg absolute inset-0 -z-20">
        <img
            src="/assets/hero-bg.png"
            alt="Villa Tahfizh background"
            loading="eager"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        />
    </div>
    <div
        class="hero-overlay absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-dark/85 via-primary/75 to-dark/85"
    >
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-32 md:py-48 text-white max-w-3xl">
        <h1
            class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-[3.25rem] font-bold font-heading mb-6 leading-tight"
        >
            Wakaf Lahan untuk<br />
            <span class="text-accent-light">Penjaga Al-Qur'an</span>
        </h1>

        <p
            class="text-lg md:text-xl opacity-90 mb-12 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl"
        >
            1300m² untuk pusat tahfizh generasi Qur'ani — Setiap ayat yang
            dipelajari, setiap huruf yang dihafal, menjadi aliran pahala jariyah
            bagi para pewakaf.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mb-12">
            <a
                href="#wakaf"
                class="btn btn-pulse inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-primary-dark text-white rounded-xl font-heading font-semibold text-lg shadow-[0_4px_14px_rgba(13,124,61,0.35)] hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-transform"
            >
                ❤️ Wakaf Sekarang
            </a>
            <a
                href="#progress"
                class="btn inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-white/15 border-2 border-white/40 backdrop-blur-md text-white rounded-xl font-heading font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-white/25 hover:border-white/60 hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all"
            >
                📊 Lihat Progress
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-6 opacity-85 text-sm md:text-base">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span
                    class="w-5 h-5 bg-accent text-dark rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] shrink-0"
                    >✓</span
                >
                <span>Legal Yayasan Resmi</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span
                    class="w-5 h-5 bg-accent text-dark rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] shrink-0"
                    >✓</span
                >
                <span>Terdaftar Kemenkumham</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span
                    class="w-5 h-5 bg-accent text-dark rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] shrink-0"
                    >✓</span
                >
                <span>Terverifikasi & Transparan</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
